m som er for syke til \u00e5 sendes i drosje, men ikke s\u00e5 syk at de trenger ambulanse. Vi h\u00e5per dette tilbudet vil bidra til at pasienter blir skrevet ut tidligere p\u00e5 dagen, sier Heimstad."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4a60f85321bc1d127dbe9e30937417fbf272cdcb3ceab05f4280076ce45680bd"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-03T21:51:39.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital iverksetter n\u00e5 flere tiltak for \u00e5 f\u00e5 utskrivningsklare pasienter raskere ut av sykehuset."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article14166430.ece/xj7otl/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Syketransport9832.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6e96e99e6778d5a13e73345e744eb4c15ea1865b.jpg?597dc5f0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Slik skal St. Olav l\u00f8se akutt-kaoset -adressa.no", "Fra seng til stressless", "Refs av fylkeslegen", "- Nedsl\u00e5ende", "Flere tiltak"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "6e96e99e6778d5a13e73345e744eb4c15ea1865b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["pasienter raskere", "pasient", "utskrivningsklare pasienter raskere", "l\u00f8se akutt-kaoset", "utskrivningsklare pasienter"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["st. olav", "orkdal og trondheim", "olavs hospital", "st. olavs hospital"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "midt-norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["morten dragsnes", "runa heimstad"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "v